Hi all, sorta biggish change coming to Launcher soon (already in master) - it has to do with how Organizations/Workspaces work in Launcher. Not going to tell you all what it is to test out how intuitive it is :slightly_smiling_face:
This is just the first step of some much bigger changes to Organizations, Settings, and ACLs! If you have questions about this change or what is to come, please ask away in <#CLBGA5A7K|>
